Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:11.11,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}灑落在 舒睡的睫毛間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:26.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}讓輕拂的風吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:38.97,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}枝葉間滑落的陽光 映襯你的睡顏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:38.97,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:45.31,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雖是個平凡無奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:52.92,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艷麗的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:03:00.39,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是與你邂逅的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.93,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我並非孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:10.70,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因為 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
